## uname: Darwin bm-xserve09.build.mozilla.org 8.8.4 Darwin Kernel Version 8.8.4: Sun Oct 29 15:26:54 PST 2006; root:xnu-792.16.4.obj~1/RELEASE_I386 i386 i386
